MULTI-PLAYING POLICY

Multi-playing means controlling more than one character at the same time.

Allowed:
  - A second character used at different times (not simultaneously)
  - An alt in a different region for story purposes, if not used to spy
    on or unfairly assist another character

Not allowed:
  - Two characters online together to share loot, spying, or combat advantage
  - Using an alt to bypass bans or strikes on another account

When in doubt, ask staff before linking characters in the same scene.

